ntry where you have a permanent assignment, but you can &#8220;serve&#8221; the agency outside the United States in the manner described by Plame&#8217;s former C.I.A. colleague, Larry Johnson: &#8220;I can tell by virtue of how that [CIA from] company was set up. She was traveling overseas as a consultant in order to meet individuals who would have access, could be either agents of access, could be possible recruits to become spies for the United States in the area of about chemical, biological or nuclear weapons.&#8221; Testimony before the Senate Democratic Policy Committee on July 22, 2005 [PDF] In fact &#8220;serving outside the United States&#8221; can mean something very temporary. A grunt who spent two months in Tikrit &#8220;served&#8221; in Iraq. Condoleezza Rice travels to the Middle East in the service of the United States. If Plame traveled outside the U.S. for C.I.A business during the past five years, she was a &#8220;covert agent.&#8221; Case closed ! Keep in mind that many of the same people who refuse to believe that anyone in the Whitehouse would knowingly give up a CIA agent, also believe that the world was created in 6 days about 6000years ago. This in spite of overwhelming evidence that the earth is about a million times older than that. To many of these people logic and truth are just tools to be manipulated to suit an agenda. How they arive at their agenda I do not pretend to understand, but truth has nothing to do with it. I am not going to point fingers or call names. However, I deal in facts, not speculation or propaganda. I would like to see documents proving the following assertions (or at least news articles mentioning them, not blogs or opinion pieces): 1) Valerie Plame made three different assertions concerning who suggested her husband&#8217;s trip to Niger. I&#8217;ve been following this case from the beginning, and I&#8217;ve never heard that. 2) The 9/11 Commission Report cast significant doubts over all of Joe Wilson&#8217;s find